Here's a simple HTML template for a personal portfolio page:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        /* Basic Reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        nav {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        nav ul {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            list-style: none;
        }

        nav ul li {
            margin: 0 15px;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #3498db;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        h2 {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .project {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .project h3 {
            color: #3498db;
        }

        .skills {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .skill {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        /* Contact Form */
        form {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        input, textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        button {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav ul {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            nav ul li {
                margin: 5px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>John Doe</h1>
        <p>Web Developer & Designer</p>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="#projects">Projects</a></li>
            <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <section id="about">
            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <p>Hello! I'm John, a passionate web developer with 5 years of experience creating modern and responsive websites. I specialize in front-end development and have a strong background in UI/UX design.</p>
            <p>I believe in clean code, intuitive design, and creating websites that not only look great but also provide an excellent user experience.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="projects">
            <h2>My Projects</h2>

            <div class="project">
                <h3>E-commerce Website</h3>
                <p>A fully responsive e-commerce platform built with React and Node.js. Features include user authentication, product filtering, cart functionality, and payment integration.</p>
                <p><a href="#">View Project</a></p>
            </div>

            <div class="project">
                <h3>Portfolio Website</h3>
                <p>A clean and modern portfolio website for a photographer. Built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript with a focus on showcasing high-resolution images and smooth transitions.</p>
                <p><a href="#">View Project</a></p>
            </div>

            <div class="project">
                <h3>Task Management App</h3>
                <p>A productivity web app that helps users manage tasks and projects. Built with Vue.js and Firebase, featuring real-time updates and collaborative features.</p>
                <p><a href="#">View Project</a></p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="skills">
            <h2>Skills</h2>
            <div class="skills">
                <span class="skill">HTML5</span>
                <span class="skill">CSS3</span>
                <span class="skill">JavaScript</span>
                <span class="skill">React</span>
                <span class="skill">Node.js</span>
                <span class="skill">Vue.js</span>
                <span class="skill">Responsive Design</span>
                <span class="skill">UI/UX Design</span>
                <span class="skill">Git</span>
                <span class="skill">WordPress</span>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="contact">
            <h2>Contact Me</h2>
            <form>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="name">Name</label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email">Email</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="message">Message</label>
                    <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
                </div>

                <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
            </form>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 John Doe. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>
            <a href="https://github.com/johndoe">GitHub</a> | 
            <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/johndoe">LinkedIn</a> | 
            <a href="mailto:john@example.com">john@example.com</a>
        </p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
```

This template includes:

1. A header with your name and title
2. Navigation menu
3. About Me section
4. Projects section with sample projects
5. Skills section with a visual list of skills
6. Contact form
7. Footer with copyright and social links

The CSS is included in the `<style>` tag in the head section for simplicity. For a real portfolio, you might want to move it to a separate CSS file.

This template is responsive and will look good on both desktop and mobile devices. You can customize the colors, fonts, and content to match your personal brand.
